Tailwind Css :

- It is css framework made up of utility classes.


Install Tailwind Css Process :

- node -v :for node js version/node js install or not
  cd documenets  : create project folder.
  cd tuts : tuts : project folder name.
  mkdir ninjafood
  cd ninjafood
  code.


Open Terminal folder : New Terminal 
- npm init -y : Enter after package.json show.
- npm install tailwindcss : Install tailwindcss
- npx tailwindcss init --full : for create tailwind.config.js


- npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch  : Build your css 

- npm install -D @tailwindcss/forms 

- npm run dev -ddd

Install Extension : 

1. Tailwind CSS IntelliSense
2. PostCSS Language Support
3. Live Server



Shortcode Visual code : 

1. a*4>img


Padding Code :

1. px-0 : padding-left:0 , padding-right:0  .. x means : left,right
2. py-0 : padding-top:0 ,  padding-bottom:0 .. y means : top,bottom
3. p-px	padding: 1px;


Margin Code :

1. mx-0 : margin-left:0 , margin-right:0  .. x means : left,right
2. my-0 : margin-top:0 ,  margin-bottom:0 .. y means : top,bottom
3. m-px	margin: 1px;
4. mx-px	margin-left: 1px;
			margin-right: 1px;
5. my-px	margin-top: 1px;
			margin-bottom: 1px;


Width code for desktop and extra large screen :

1. lg:w-2/3 xl:w-2/3




